race.description: Williams Seeders Country Boosted Maiden Plate
race.comment: CRASHMYPLAYA (2) has been knocking on the door for quite some time, adding another narrow minor placing to the last time when beaten a head at Inverell. Should settle closer from the kind draw and is the one to beat. INVINCIBOO (3) showed good early speed last start over this track and trip, only to be collared late. Doesn't need to improve much to get the verdict. EVONY (7) improved last start when second-up from a break, finishing 1.2 lengths adrift in fourth over 1400m at Inverell. Peaking now and is ready to hit top form. KAHU (4) hasn't trialled this time in work, having his latest public outing back in July, but he creates some interest on debut.
